<header
  class="mb-12 sm:mb-20 md:mb-28 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-8 border-b border-white/5 pb-10"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <div class="reveal-text flex items-center gap-3 mb-6" style="--delay: 0ms">
      <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-aux-secondary"></span>
      <span
        class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-aux-secondary"
      >
        El Equipo
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-hidden leading-[0.9]"> 
      <h2
        class="reveal-title text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter text-white"
        style="--delay: 150ms"
      >
        Maestros de <br />
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="overflow-hidden pb-2 leading-[0.9]">
      <h2
        class="reveal-title text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter"
        style="--delay: 300ms"
      >
        <span class="ink-gradient">
          la Tinta
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <p
      class="reveal-text mt-8 text-base md:text-xl text-gray-400 font-light max-w-xl leading-relaxed"
      style="--delay: 500ms"
    >
      No solo tatuamos, creamos legado. Cada artista aporta una visión técnica
      única, fusionando tradición y vanguardia en cada trazo.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="hidden md:block pb-2 reveal-button" style="--delay: 700ms">
    <a
      href="#booking"
      class="group relative flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-3 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase overflow-hidden rounded-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:text-aux-secondary"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:border-aux-secondary/50 group-hover:bg-white/10"
      >
      </div>

      <span class="relative z-10">Agendar Cita</span>

      <span
        class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full border border-white/20 group-hover:border-aux-secondary group-hover:bg-aux-secondary group-hover:text-primarybg transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-3 h-3 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .ink-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(
      110deg,
      var(--color-primary) 0%,
      var(--color-secondary) 40%,
      var(--color-aux-primary) 50%, 
      var(--color-secondary) 60%,
      var(--color-primary) 100%
    );
    background-size: 200% auto;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    animation: shine 5s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shine {
    to { background-position: -200% center; }
  }

  .reveal-text {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    filter: blur(4px);
    transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    transition-delay: var(--delay);
    will-change: transform, opacity, filter;
  }

  :global(.is-visible) .reveal-text {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    filter: blur(0);
  }

  .reveal-button {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    transition-delay: var(--delay);
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  :global(.is-visible) .reveal-button {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .reveal-title {
    display: block; 
    transform: translateY(110%) rotate(2deg); 
    opacity: 0; 
    transform-origin: left bottom;
    transition: transform 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1), opacity 0.5s ease;
    transition-delay: var(--delay);
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  :global(.is-visible) .reveal-title {
    transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>